6. Arrays.sort()

Java provides a built-in sorting method.

import java.util.Arrays;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int arr[] = {5, 3, 8, 4, 2};

        Arrays.sort(arr);

        System.out.println(Arrays.toString(arr));
    }
}

Output

[2, 3, 4, 5, 8]

Time Complexity

O(n log n)